nghua.edu.cn</p>\n\n\n<p>\n所在单位：电子工程系\n</p>\n\n\n\n<p>\n办公地点：清华大学电子工程系 罗姆楼8-110\n</p>\n\n<p>\n性别：男\n</p>\n\n\n\n<p>\n在职信息：在职\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!--学科-->\n\n<script> var _tsites_com_view_mode_type_=8;</script>\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/tsites/tsitesencrypt.js\"></script>\n\n\n\n</div>\n<!---基本信息结束------><!---其他联系方式开始------><div class=\"p_l_nr\">\n                <h1 class=\"t_qtlxfs_t\">其他联系方式<span>Other Contact Information</span></h1>\n                <div class=\"t_qtlxfs_nr\">\n                    <p>\n                    邮编 : \n                    100084</p>\n                    <p>\n                    通讯/办公地址 : \n                    清华大学电子工程系 罗姆楼 3-102/103</p>\n                    <p>\n                    邮箱 : \n                    zhoubowen@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                </div>\n                </div>\n<!---其他联系方式结束------><!---二维码开始------>\n<div class=\"p_l_nr\">\n<div class=\"t_2weima\">\n\n<!-- 下面这个div是二维码容器,ID不能变-->\n<div id=\"outputu11\" align=\"center\"><canvas width=\"174\" height=\"172\"></canvas></div>\n<!-- 下面是生成二维码调用的JS，不要动-->\n<script src=\"/system/resource/qrcode/js/jquery.qrcode.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/system/resource/qrcode/js/qrcode.js\"></script>\n<script>\nvar codeInfo = \"\" ==\"\"? window.location.href:\"\";\njQuery(function(){\n    jQuery('#outputu11').qrcode({\n        text:codeInfo,\n        render: !!document.createElement('canvas').getContext?\"canvas\":\"table\",//设置渲染方式  \n        width: 174,     //设置宽度  \n        height: 172,     //设置高度  \n        correctLevel: 2,//纠错等级  \n        background: \"#000000\",//背景颜色  \n        foreground: \"#ffffff\",//前景颜色  \n        logo:\"\"//图像logo\n    });\n})\n</script> </div></div><!---二维码结束------><!---二维码开始------>\n<div class=\"t_link\">\n</div><!---二维码结束------></div>\n   </div>\n<div class=\"p_right\"><!---教师个人简历开始------>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"p_r_nr \" style=\"border-top: #05b4a3 4px solid\">\n<h1 class=\"t_grjj\">个人简介<span>Personal Profile</span></h1>\n                <div class=\"t_grjj_nr\">\n                    <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; \"></p><p>Bowen Zhou is a Huiyan Chair Professor at Tsinghua University, a tenured Professor in the Department of Electronic Engineering, the Director of the Center for Collaborative and Cognitive Interaction Intelligence (C3I), and the Founder of Xianyuan Technology. He is also a Fellow of IEEE and CAAI.</p>\n<p>Professor Zhou brings a wealth of experience from both cutting-edge research and industry. He previously served as Director of the AI Foundation Lab at IBM Research, Chief Scientist of the IBM Watson Group, IBM Distinguished Engineer, Senior Vice President of JD.com, Chairman of the JD Group Technology Committee, and President of JD Cloud &amp; AI. In 2022, he returned to academia from industry.</p>\n<p>His research interests include speech and natural language processing, multimodal and knowledge representation, understanding, generation, reasoning, human-computer dialogue, and trustworthy AI. He has published over 100 papers with more than 21,000 citations and holds dozens of domestic and international patents.</p>\n<p>He proposed a self-attentive multi-head fusion mechanism for natural language representation, which later became one of the core ideas of the Transformer architecture and has been cited over 2,000 times by papers such as Transformer and GAT. He also proposed two natural language generation model architectures and algorithms in the field of AIGC, which have been cited more than 3,000 times.</p>\n<p>Lab homepage: <a href=\"http://c3i.ee.tsinghua.edu.cn/\">http://c3i.ee.tsinghua.edu.cn</a> (including latest publications)</p>\n<p><br></p><p></p>\n                </div>\n               \n                \n             \n</div>\n<!---教师个人简历结束------><!---教育经历开始------>\n<div class=\"slideTxtBox\" style=\"background: url(/_ts/dzxzwmb01/images/t_r_zsbg.png) #fff no-repeat right top; padding-bottom: 15px; padding-top: 20px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 0px\">\n<div class=\"hd\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"on\">教育经历<span>Education Background</span> </li>\n<li>工作经历<span>Work Experience</span></li>\n</ul></div>\n<div class=\"bd\">\n<ul class=\"t_edu_nr\"><a>\n<ul class=\"jyjlulu17\">\n<li>中国科学技术大学</li>\n<li>电子信息工程</li>\n\n<li style=\"background: none;\">学士学位</li>\n</ul>\n</a>\n<a>\n<ul class=\"jyjlulu17\">\n<li>中国科学院</li>\n<li>信息和信号处理</li>\n\n<li style=\"background: none;\">硕士学位</li>\n</ul>\n</a>\n<a>\n<ul class=\"jyjlulu17\">\n<li>美国科罗拉多大学</li>\n<li>电子和计算机工程</li>\n\n<li style=\"background: none;\">博士学位</li>\n</ul>\n</a>\n\n<script>\njQuery(document).ready(function(){\n  var lastliobj = jQuery(\"ul.jyjlulu17\").each(function(){\n      var ulobj = jQuery(this);\n      var allli = ulobj.children();\n     if(allli.length>0){\n    allli[allli.length-1].style.background=\"none\"; \n}\n  });\n});\n</script> \n<style>\n.lxxstarttime{\nwidth:75px;\n}\n\n</style>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"t_edu_nr\" style=\"display: none;\"><a>\n<ul class=\"gzjlu18\"> \n<li>北京衔远有限公司</li>\n<li style=\"background: none;\">创始人</li>\n</ul>\n</a>\n<a>\n<ul class=\"gzjlu18\"> \n<li>京东集团</li>\n<li style=\"background: none;\">京东集团高级副总裁、京东集团技术委员会主席、京东云与AI总裁、京东人工智能研究院创始院长</li>\n</ul>\n</a>\n<a>\n<ul class=\"gzjlu18\"> \n<li>IBM</li>\n<li style=\"background: none;\">Director of AI Foundations Labs, IBM Research；Chief Scientist of IBM Watson Group；IBM Distinguished Engineer</li>\n</ul>\n</a>\n\n\n\n<script>\njQuery(document).ready(function(){\n  var lastliobj = jQuery(\"ul.gzjlu18\").each(function(){\n      var ulobj = jQuery(this);\n      var allli = ulobj.children();\n      if(allli.length>0){\n    allli[allli.length-1].style.background=\"none\"; \n}\n     \n  });\n});\n</script>  </ul></div><script type=\"text/javascript\">jQuery(\".slideTxtBox\").slide();</script></div><!---教育经历结束------><!---社会兼职开开始------>\n<div class=\"slideTxtBox2\" style=\"background: url(/_ts/dzxzwmb01/images/body_topbg2.png) #fff no-repeat right top; padding-bottom: 15px; 